      <div class="blog-card-right">
        
        <span name="post_summary" id="post_summary">
          <p class="card-text"><p>I gave AI coding tools like GitHub Copilot a try
and found them subtly valuable.
They're not replacements but augmentations for skilled practitioners
who can verify their output.
Incorrect outputs can spark creative solutions,
making these tools powerful.
So, no, AI won't take our jobs,
but will supercharge our skills. üöÄüë©‚Äçüíªü§ñ</p>
